      <div class="excerpt">
        <p>Last Thursday, the Governor released and signed Executive Order 50, Executive Action to Prevent Gun Violence. The details to the order can be found here-<a href="https://governor.virginia.gov/newsroom/newsarticle?articleId=13032">https://governor.virginia.gov/newsroom/newsarticle?articleId=13032</a></p>
        
